column1: Heteropteran data from Threlfall et al Journal of Applied Ecology 'Increasing biodiversity in urban green spaces through simple vegetation interventions'
For data collection methods see above paper.
spp = species. Point = green space site (n=39). Rep = plot within each green space.

Also, see Mata et al for further details: Mata, L., Threlfall, C.G., Williams, N.S.G., Hahs, A., Malipatil, M., Stork, N. & Livesley, S.J. (in press) Conserving herbivorous and predatory insects in urban green spaces. Scientific Reports, accepted 13th Dec 2016.
